FPGA Bitstream Tests in Order:

1) clock_tests/pulse_clock_test_bitstream_v1 = output just slow clock 
2) clock_tests/pulse_clock_test_bitstream_v2 = output just fast clock with bad waveform (12.5 MHz)
3) clock_tests/pulse_clock_test_bitstream_v3 = output just fast clock with better waveform (12.5 MHz)

4) cpu_fpga_comm_tests/cpu_fpga_comm_on_off_and_switch_clk_freq = simple testing of cpu to fpga communication by simple on/off toggle of clock output
5) cpu_fpga_comm_tests/cpu_fpga_comm_simple_switch_clk_freq = added the ability to switch output clock frequency as well as the on/off toggle

6) bitstream_v1 = program now also acts as a shared memory, allowing writes from the cpu and then sending the data when the cpu sends another signal
7) bitstream_v2 = added negated output and clock for testing
8) bitstream_v3 = added negated clock for testing, with 2 versions for low-driven outputs or not

